Package vehicles

Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
vehicles.Vehicle
Direct Known Subclasses:
Lorry, Tanker, TimberTruck, TowTruck
public abstract class Vehicle extends Object
Class storing data of vehicles that are moving inside simulations World, every child of Vehicle has its own type. acceptedPointType corresponds to points types that vehicle can cooperate with.

    • moveVehicle

      public int[] moveVehicle​(int worldSize)
      Move vehicle one field in random direction, if random directions are not possible it generates them again until valid direction is generated, after moving the vehicle, it's money is decreased by its transportCost
      Parameters:
      worldSize - world size of World instance, to prevent generating impossible coordinates
      Returns:
      Returns list of newly generated coordinates {x, y}
